10
00:00:20.940 --> 00:00:23.640
The four layers are: the
network access layer,

11
00:00:23.640 --> 00:00:26.310
the internet layer,
the transport layer,

12
00:00:26.310 --> 00:00:27.900
and the application layer.

13
00:00:28.900 --> 00:00:31.305
Knowing how the TCP/IP model
organizes network activity

14
00:00:31.305 --> 00:00:32.760
allows security professionals to

15
00:00:32.760 --> 00:00:35.220
monitor and secure
